title: Street Fighter 6 Akuma Official Teaser Trailer
description:
The legendary Akuma will consume all hope, fear, and nothingness when he comes to Street Fighter 6 this spring. Find him in the new World Tour area, Gokuento, where you may ask him to be your Master...if you dare.

Owners of the Deluxe and Ultimate Edition or the Year 1 Character Pass and Ultimate Pass of Street Fighter 6 will obtain Akuma when he releases.

title: Rise Of The Ronin GameSpot Hands On Preview
description: Rise of the Ronin's opening two hours offer an exciting glimpse of its measured combat and the possibilities of Team Ninja's newfound approach to player freedom.

title: Dragon's Dogma 2 Everything To Know
description:
It’s been twelve years since Capcom released Dragon’s Dogma, in which we took up the mantle of the Arisen on our quest to defeat a fantasy Italian dragon. Now, with the release of the sequel imminent, we’re taking a closer look at the upcoming hack-and-slash adventure. Here’s everything you need to know about Dragon’s Dogma II.
